 />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3MBSwwYghfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3MBSwwYghfE&d=zM35jLS05zISECKmFrxpgAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=434a9099\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3MBSwwYghfE</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"呢個學生緊係做埋做埋好多陰質嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"痴線，加速完都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599e53874b45e9b373c74ffb9479ab635f2cbdc2","tid":718884,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"703f5252062b9497717dbb2f255a74bd22baae2d","tid":718884,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"完整片段:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/agFMN8tNL64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FagFMN8tNL64&d=zM35jLS05zISECKmFrxpgAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=355a15ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/agFMN8tNL64</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/06/27/1419323-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F1419323-XXL.jpg&h=3b7b8f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/06/27/1419325-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F1419325-XXL.jpg&h=d4462ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n大陸廣東省近日發生一起駭人的車禍事件，一輛大巴士在高速公路上失控翻覆，造成3死9傷，初步調查後是路面有油汙，導致遊覽車打滑，加上左輪胎爆胎才造成側翻，現場畫面曝光後也引起網友討論。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，一輛遊覽車在高速公路的隧道口前失控打滑，右側車身更當場分離，車身撞擊到地面的瞬間，整排乘客當場被甩出車外，接著還被車身重壓在車底。<br />\n<br />\n監視器畫面曝光後，由於畫面相當驚悚，也引起大批網友討論，紛紛留言「幸好大卡車來得及剎車，不然後果更不堪設想」、「一側翻，車窗裡掉出一堆人」、「要是繫了安全帶，一個都不會死」不過，也有網友認為「椅子都甩出來了，安全帶有用？為什麼不質疑車的質量問題？」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"RIP⋯⋯好慘"},{"pid":"8f9f241ac4a87f44118471db63fc974dde8acc02","tid